        <updateDate>2022-04-15T18:52:46Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p>This bill prohibits withholding federal education funds from an otherwise eligible recipient (e.g., educational agencies, schools, and institutions of higher education) because the recipient does not require students or employees to be vaccinated against COVID-19.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
